sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend App<br/>(Teams / Portal)
    participant Entra as Microsoft Entra ID
    participant AS as Hosted<br/>Agent Service
    participant SDK as CopilotClient<br/>(Agents SDK)
    participant CS as Microsoft<br/>Copilot Studio
    participant API as Internal<br/>Enterprise API

    rect rgb(220, 225, 245)
        Note over User, Entra: Phase 1 — Authentication
        User ->>+ FE: ❶ Sign In
        FE ->>+ Entra: ❷ Authenticate User (OIDC)
        Note right of Entra: Conditional Access<br/>Policies Enforced
        Entra -->>- FE: ❸ User Access Token (JWT)
    end

    rect rgb(215, 240, 220)
        Note over FE, AS: Phase 2 — Request Submission
        FE ->>+ AS: ❹ Prompt + User Token (Bearer)
        Note right of AS: Validate JWT<br/>(signature, claims, scopes)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 210)
        Note over AS, CS: Phase 3 — Agent Orchestration (via CopilotClient SDK)
        AS ->>+ Entra: ❺ OBO Token Exchange<br/>(CopilotStudio.Copilots.Invoke scope)
        Entra -->>- AS: ❻ Power Platform Access Token
        AS ->>+ SDK: ❼ Create CopilotClient<br/>(token provider function)
        SDK ->>+ CS: ❽ StartConversationAsync<br/>(SSE streaming)
        CS -->> SDK: ❾ Bot Greeting (streamed activities)
        SDK ->> CS: ❿ AskQuestionAsync(prompt)<br/>(SSE streaming)
        CS -->>- SDK: ⓫ Bot Reply (streamed activities)
        SDK -->>- AS: ⓬ IAsyncEnumerable[Activity]
        Note right of CS: Agent decides if<br/>tool invocation needed
    end

    rect rgb(235, 220, 245)
        Note over AS, API: Phase 4 — Delegated API Call (OBO Flow)
        AS ->>+ Entra: ⓭ OBO Token Exchange<br/>(Enterprise API scope)
        Entra -->>- AS: ⓮ Delegated Access Token
        AS ->>+ API: ⓯ Call API using OBO Token<br/>(GET /api/me)
        API -->>- AS: ⓰ API Response (user-specific data)
    end

    rect rgb(250, 225, 220)
        Note over User, API: Phase 5 — Response Delivery
        AS -->>- FE: ⓱ Combined Response<br/>(agent reply + enterprise data)
        FE -->> User: ⓲ Display Response
    end
